.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people have 5 different jobs:  pilot, dancer, nurse, entrepreneur, fisherman
The people have 5 different hobbies: filmmaking, magic-tricks, hiking, gardening, board-games
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: comedy, action, epic, musical, disaster
There 5 different types of food: pilotmaster, asparagus, cauliflower, cucumber, watermelon
City: rome, venice, nizza, san-francisco, colone
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the nurse
2. the person who's hobby is swedish is the person traveling to nizza
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person watching musical movies
4. the dancer is on the left of the entrepreneur
5. the dancer is the person watching action movies
6. the person eating cauliflower is the person traveling to venice
7. the fisherman is the person eating asparagus
8. the person watching epic movies is in the middle
9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left
10. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome
11. the person traveling to colones is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus
12. the person eating pilotmaster is the person watching comedy movies
13. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person eating cucumber
14. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the pilot
15. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Job		|    fisherman	|     pilot	|      nurse	|     dancer	|     entrepreneur	|
| Hobby	|   gardening	|    magic-tricks	|    filmmaking	|    hiking	|    swedish	|
| City		|     rome	|    colone	|     venice	|     san-francisco	|      nizza	|
| Movie-Genre	|    disaster	|     musical	|     epic	|    action	|      comedy	|
| Food		|   asparagus	|    watermelon	|  cauliflower	|    cucumber	|   pilotmaster	|
